<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>in an instant • on the instant</xh5><p> <i>in an instant—</i>in a moment: Our ship was <u>in an instant</u> full of these swarthy gentlemen quite naked.</p><p> <i>on the instant—</i>at once; immediately: When you shut the doors of this grotto, it becomes <u>on the instant</u>, from a luminous room, a camera obscura.</p> </entry>
